OL,6,FTheatr Clwyd in will be given
OL,7,Finvestment through the UK Government's
OL,8,FLevelling Up funding, Chancellor
OL,9,FJeremy Hunt announced in the Budget on
OL,10,FWednesday, .
OL,12,FMr Hunt pledged #1.6 million from the
OL,13,Fgovernment in to help with the
OL,14,Frenovation of the theatre.
OL,16,FWork has been underway on the site
OL,17,Fsince January 2023 with the renovation
OL,18,Fset to be completed next year.
