OL,6,FAs the building became older it faced
OL,7,Fissues with a burst water pipe
OL,8,Fflooding the dressing rooms and then
OL,9,Fsnow falling through one of the
OL,10,Fceilings.
OL,12,FThe theatre was also used as a blood
OL,13,Fbank during the .
OL,15,FWith events now back whilst the
OL,16,Frenovation is underway, Theatr Clwyd
OL,17,Fis Wales' largest producing theatre -
OL,18,Fa theatre which creates its own shows.
