OL,6,FIt is set to stage numerous plays in
OL,7,Fthe coming months, including various
OL,8,Fadaptations of Shakespeare, as well as
OL,9,Fmore contemporary shows and comedy
OL,10,Fgigs.
OL,12,FWelcoming the Chancellor's
OL,13,Fannouncement, Conservative Vale of
OL,14,FClwyd MP Dr James Davies said: "This
OL,15,Fis absolutely fantastic news for
OL,16,FTheatr Clwyd and everyone who uses it.
OL,17,FThe theatre is a very well known and
OL,18,Fsuccessful facility in Mold."
